    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines an IPv6 unicast address format that is globally unique and is intended for local communications, usually inside of a site.  These addresses are not expected to be routable on the global Internet. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
